He intro­ duced his law in this ostentatious manner, as if to show that he would release people though you had thought fit to im­ prison them.
Does any one think a law beneficial to the commonwealth, which is to overrule the judgment of a legal tribunal, and which will require persons not on their oaths to rescind the verdicts of sworn jurors?
